
paas nahi aaungi door chali jaungi
chedungi main naa tujhe
ek pappi dede mujhe
main tanaha akeli rahungi kaise ye darde judai sahungi main kaise
aa mujhako tham le masti kaa jaam le
pyasi jawani hai thodi diwani hai bahon mein lele ise
ek pappi dede mujhe
main teri yaadon ko khayalon mein basa lu
main tere chehre ko nighahon mein chhupa lu
tu mere paas hai ankhon ki pyas hai
tu meri rani hai dil ki kahani hai tu dhadakanon mein base
ek pappi dede mujhe
paas nahi ayunga door chala jaunga
chedunga main naa tujhe
ek pappi dede mujhe